{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L799","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:completionhandler:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^)()) "},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"targetCoordinate","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit